<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="foster-vt">foster <strong><em>vt</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /'fɒstə(r)/    美 /'fɔːstər/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1-encourage-promote">1.★ <strong>培养；鼓励；促进 (encourage / promote)：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Training helps to foster team spirit.
培训有助于培养团队精神。</p></div>

<h4 id="2">2.<strong>(在一定时间内) 养育；代养 (别人的孩子)</strong></h4></div>